===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Original form was {{och-l|恖}}, considered by ''{{w|Shuowen}}'' to be a {{Han compound|ls=psc|囟|心|c1=p|c2=s|t2=heart|nocap=1}}. It may also be a {{Han compound|ls=ic|囟|心|t1=fontanel|t2=heart|nocap=1}}.

{{zh-l|*囟}} started to corrupt into the unrelated {{zh-l|*田}} as early as the silk script.

